WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.374
Your customers are not waiting at the service drive anymore.

00:00:03.424 --> 00:00:06.798
They are at their desk, on a job site, in another time zone

00:00:06.848 --> 00:00:10.222
— and they are still expecting a premium service experience.

00:00:10.272 --> 00:00:13.646
In this module you will learn how to deliver that experience through every

00:00:13.696 --> 00:00:17.070
digital channel you use. Video. Text. Email. Each one is a chance to

00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:20.494
build trust — or quietly lose it.
